title: Looking for a sup main
body:
Gold adc/jg main is looking for sup main that can play most sup champs.
About me*
- I was rank 3 Varus Oce at start of this season (S8) with 80% win rate with my old duo who is no longer able to play due to her other commitments 
- I can play all adcs & assasin jgs (soloq) but ussualy stick to meta champs.
Looking forward to play with new people and hopefully find a good sup to climb with. 
If you have any questions just msg me or add my igm : Tzari
